### The Regulatory Framework

| **Standard** | **Domain** | **Requirement** |
|---|---|---|
| **IEC 62304** | Medical device software | Safety, risk management, traceability |
| **ISO 14971** | Medical device risk management | Risk analysis, mitigation, residual risk |
| **FDA Guidance** | AI/ML in medical devices | Predetermined change control, transparency |
| **MDR (EU)** | Medical Device Regulation | Clinical evaluation, post-market surveillance |
| **GDPR / HIPAA** | Data privacy | Sovereignty, consent, data protection |

**ST-T1024 is designed to meet all five frameworks by construction.**

